Tested-by: Rojewski, Cezary <cezary.rojewski@intel.com>
---
 sound/soc/codecs/tdf8532.h        | 2 +-
 sound/soc/intel/skylake/bxt-sst.c | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

